dct_title_s: Chart of the N. W. Coast of America and the N. E. Coast of Asia, explored in the years 1778 and 1779
dct_alternative_sm: Chart of the N. W. Coast of America and the N. E. Coast of Asia, explored in the years 1778 and 1779 / prepared by Lieut. Henry Roberts, under the immediate inspection of Capt. Cook.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Soundings in fathoms.
Also shows Pacific routes of Capt. James Cook in 1778 and 1779, with dates showing the distances covered.
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain.
